        <item>
            <title>Google 搜寻庆祝 25 岁生日，小车库发展成十亿人搜寻引擎</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/27/google-happy-birthday/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-happy-birthday</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/27/google-happy-birthday/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Man]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 27 Sep 2023 11:57:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生日快乐]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1195999</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今天是 Google 搜寻引擎的生日，这个搜寻引擎走过了 25 个年头。在进入 Google 首页时，可以看到缤纷的设计和图案，搜寻栏上也会出现庆祝生日的纸花动画。为了庆祝 25 岁生日，Google 推出了特别版的 Doodle，回顾了过去 25 年的发展历程，并分享了 3 个隐藏的实用技巧。</p><p>Google CEO,  Sundar Pichai 在社交媒体上表示，Google 于 1998 年由两位史丹佛大学的博士生在加州的一间车库中创立。Pichai 提到，创始人一开始就确定了 Google 的核心使命，汇整全球的资讯并提供给大众使用，为全球数十亿人解答问题。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1196006 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Google 搜索引擎</h2><p>Google 搜索引擎在 1998 年正式推出，开创了一个可以轻松在数百万个网页中寻找资讯的时代。两年后，其搜寻服务已经支援日语、韩语，以及简体和繁体中文，并于 2001 年在东京开设正式开设首间海外办公室。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196008 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>不仅仅是搜索引擎, Google 地图</h2><p>丹麦兄弟 Lars 和 Jens Rasmussen 在 2004 年于悉尼遇到两位澳洲人 Neil Gordon 及 Stephen Ma 一同研发划时代的地图技术，成就了现在的 Google 地图，亦自此开展了 Google 地图环游世界拍摄街景的旅程。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196015 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/3-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Google 翻译</h2><p>Google 翻译在翌年 2006 年推出，发展至今一直不断改良，更借助人工智能技术持续提升翻译品质，现时支援超过 40 种亚太地区语言。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196019 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/4-3-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Google Pay</h2><p>Android 于 2014 年正式推出，颠覆了亚洲地区使用手机的方式，智能手机在亚洲市场的普及程度于短时间，来超越了世界其他地区，开启了以流动通讯为主的创新科技浪潮。Google Pay 在 2011 年于美国率先推出， 而印度则是 Google Pay 在亚太区首个进驻的市场，同时亦在印度率先推出离线服务，协助当地用户节省数据流量。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196018 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196024 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/7-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196025 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/8-2.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196026 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/9-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196027 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/10-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>趁著 25 周年，Google 送出三个搜寻隐藏秘技给用户们，能够更快、更方便解答用户在生活中的疑问，分别是哼歌搜索、多种搜索以及跟 Google「揾食」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196013 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/11-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h3>哼歌搜索</h3><p>用户可以透过 Google 应用程式的「哼歌搜索」功能，只要哼唱出旋律，Google 就可以利用人工智能音乐识别技术配对相应歌曲，不妨试试唱首生日歌给 Google，除非严重走音，否则都能够顺利搜寻得到！</p><h3>多种搜索</h3><p>用户可以同时使用文字和图像搜索相关资料，例如：拍摄一张餐具组合的照片，并加入「咖啡机」作为关键词，便会出现相应的搜寻结果。</p><h3>跟 Google「揾食」</h3><p>只要在 Google 搜寻输入你想要的食物关键，字，例如：米线、炸鸡，就可以立即找到最近你的位置，并提供相关菜式的餐厅！此外，只要输入食品名称如「珍珠奶茶」，搜寻结果会显示更多相关资料，包括：食品简介、营养成分、菜式起源等等！</p><p>资料来源：Google</p><p>图片来源：Google</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
